/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:17:If the real NS-specific leverage only appears after changing the propagated quantity, changing the contradiction setup, or coupling algebraic structure to geometry or dynamics, this chain will call it irrelevant because it does not immediately improve the chosen bad term.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:27:The mission context is stronger than "the candidate uses an exact NS-looking feature." Tao's result blocks anything resting only on energy identity plus standard harmonic analysis. So the chain should demand a concrete statement of what the averaged model destroys and where that destruction enters the estimate. As written, a candidate can survive Step 1 by sounding algebraically special without showing that the specialness survives localization and actually matters quantitatively.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:29:### 4. The chain treats geometry and tensor structure mainly as contamination, which may be a false separation
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:31:Step 3 is built to strip away gains that are "really" geometric or pressure-tensor effects. That is good if the goal is a pure reformulation result. It is bad if the only real NS-specific cancellations are hybrid: exact algebraic form plus alignment, or rewrite plus concentrated tube geometry, or rewrite plus tensor structure. The chain risks discarding the only live mechanisms because they are not pure enough.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:51:- It never says which bottleneck is mission-central. Is it the De Giorgi truncated pressure contribution, a local-energy flux term, a vorticity stretching localization, or some projected interaction? Those are not interchangeable. A rewrite that helps one may do nothing for the others.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:64:- The natural test family is too familiar. Lamb-vector, projected form, and vorticity transport are exactly the rewrites one would expect to collapse back to the same structure unless some additional mechanism is injected. The mission context already suggests that at least part of this family has been effectively stress-tested.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:78:- It treats geometry, near-Beltrami structure, and tensor effects as things to subtract away before believing a gain. That is too purity-driven for this mission. The live beyond-De-Giorgi mechanism may be hybrid rather than purely algebraic.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:81:- The handoff logic is too clean. If a rewrite only helps when combined with local geometry, that may be evidence of the correct mechanism, not evidence that the reformulation chain failed.
